data.title: About postmand_b
data.meta_description:
Update 21th of aug. 2012: Going to Toronto Canada in a few days. First time ever across the atlantic. Hoping to be able to add some pics.
	
	I there :-)
	
	38 yo. scandinavian (Denmark) guy just here to browse pics. And post some myself. I' not a pro, but just enjoy taking pics, and even more when others like them too :o)
	Nature is the love of my life.
	
	Looking for friends in Alaska and Canada, or north america.
	Got a serious crush on the nature and wildlife in those parts, and hope to live there one day.
	Am a huge DICK PROENNEKE fan.
	Have a huntinglicence and riffles, but havent hunted yet.
	
	
	August 2011: FINALLY got a new cam. A NIKON D5000 :o)
	
	OF CAUSE LOOKING FOR FRIENDS IN THE PLACES BELOW: 
	Thinking about moving to Canada or Alaska (us), due to my facination by the nature and wildlife of these arears.
